{"tid":1585952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【意見】對手足以武制暴，我有一個意見","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:13:40.000Z","uid":282280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05a90c8a207b0b287bb1f12c3dc1d34e1092d397","tid":1585952,"uid":282280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"嗨，大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有人話唔應該係對家鬧下我地既前提下動手，<br />\n當然果班屌手足既人睇唔哂全部，<br />\n或者記者鏡頭影唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 手足下次以武制暴既同時，<br />\n大叫條友做過d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n務求令到手足當時有理有據地制暴（太多直播），<br />\n文宣後其最多都係解釋返成件事，<br />\n但如果主要靠文宣後期「補飛」，<br />\n會令人覺得你為自己掩飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">以下句式需要於制暴中不停重覆</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例：<br />\n1. （一邊打一邊叫）打女仔？！打女仔呀嗱？！打得你咁爽？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.（一邊打一邊叫）拎刀𠝹市民？！𠝹呀嗱？！𠝹比我睇？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. （一邊打一邊叫）拎棍扑記者？！扑呀嗱？！仲扑唔撚扑？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（當然極速秒怪果d唔需要）</span><br />\n<br />\n大概係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個方法可以令附近既人/自己理性地進行制暴<br />\n因為你需要比自己一個還擊既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">順便提一提，有意見請以比意見既態度提出，唔係係咪都屌左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n</span><br />\n以上純粹鳩噏，歡迎提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯屌細力d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港  時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9914838303863325038ba4e580b9613f74d91c3b","tid":1585952,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:10:29.000Z","msg":"提出建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08619c62dbf857b5e04c893d26bbe77149a62393","tid":1585952,"uid":75461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:12:32.000Z","msg":"還緊拖最緊要快同狠，未必有時間做。不過都係好提議"},{"pid":"517bcc0ca34d4d87e81eda871b206078fea8d452","tid":1585952,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}